title: HERE'S LUCY -- with Jack Benny, George Burns, Mary Livingstone
description:
Jack Benny had gotten his wife Mary Livingstone out of a 12-year retirement
temporarily in 1970 for his TV special "Jack Benny's 20th TV Anniversary", in which she played herself in a sketch. From that same year unfortunately only Mary's voice is heard in this Here's Lucy episode, in which she dubbed over Lucy playing Mary in a segment in which Jack and Lucy are re-enacting a brief part of one of his 1940s radio show episodes.
